[{"type":"info","header":"","html":"<p><strong>嫌步骤多?</strong> 直接运行 <code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">bash ~/workshop/08-create-evaluators.sh</code> 即可,它打包了\"复制源码 → 注册 → 部署 → 授权 Bedrock 权限\"的完整流程。下面是逐步展开。</p>"},{"type":"warning","header":"","html":"<p>必须 <code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">rm -rf</code> + <code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">cp -r</code> 整个目录,不能只 cp <code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">lambda_function.py</code> 和 <code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">pyproject.toml</code>。<code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">agentcore add evaluator</code> 的 scaffold 会重建 codeLocation 目录,丢掉 <code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">shared/</code> 和 <code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">evaluators/</code> 子模块,部署后 Lambda 启动时会报 <code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">No module named 'shared'</code>。</p>"},{"type":"warning","header":"如果部署报 LogGroup already exists","html":"<p>在<strong>同一账号重复跑过本 workshop</strong>时，可能残留上次的评估器日志组，导致部署回滚并报 <code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">AWS::Logs::LogGroup '/aws/lambda/hrassistant-eval-...' already exists</code>。先删掉残留日志组再重试即可（全新临时账号不会遇到）：</p><div class=\"CodeBlock-module_codeBlock__LKx5X CodeBlock-module_hasCopyAction__WMrpt\"><pre dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: black; font-family: var(--font-family-monospace-q47m7k, Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, 'Courier Prime', Courier, 'Courier New', monospace); font-size: 13px; text-align: left; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: normal; line-height: 1.5; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; padding: 1em; margin: 0px; overflow: auto; box-sizing: border-box;\"><code class=\"language-bash\" style=\"white-space: pre; color: black; background: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: left; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: normal; line-height: inherit; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none;\"><code style=\"color: black; background: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: left; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: normal; line-height: inherit; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; float: left; padding-right: var(--space-scaled-xl-gt502a, 24px);\"><span class=\"react-syntax-highlighter-line-number\" style=\"opacity: 0.38;\">1\n</span><span class=\"react-syntax-highlighter-line-number\" style=\"opacity: 0.38;\">2\n</span><span class=\"react-syntax-highlighter-line-number\" style=\"opacity: 0.38;\">3\n</span><span class=\"react-syntax-highlighter-line-number\" style=\"opacity: 0.38;\">4\n</span></code><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 119, 170);\">for</span><span> </span><span class=\"token for-or-select\" style=\"color: rgb(238, 153, 0);\">FN</span><span> </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 119, 170);\">in</span><span> hrassistant-eval-thelma_rag_quality hrassistant-eval-mtg_goal_success</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">;</span><span> </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 119, 170);\">do</span><span>\n</span><span>  aws logs delete-log-group --log-group-name </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 153, 0);\">\"/aws/lambda/</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(238, 153, 0);\">$FN</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 153, 0);\">\"</span><span> --region us-west-2 </span><span class=\"token file-descriptor\" style=\"color: rgb(238, 153, 0); font-weight: bold;\">2</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(154, 110, 58);\">&gt;</span><span>/dev/null </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(154, 110, 58);\">||</span><span> </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 85);\">true</span><span>\n</span><span></span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 119, 170);\">done</span><span>\n</span>agentcore deploy --yes</code></pre><span class=\"awsui_root_xjuzf_11ym3_559 CodeBlock-module_copyAction__E7A8w\"><span class=\"awsui_trigger_xjuzf_11ym3_594\" id=\":r2r:\"><button class=\"CopyButton-module_styledButton__sS63U awsui_button_vjswe_1ufnn_157 awsui_variant-normal_vjswe_1ufnn_206 awsui_button-no-text_vjswe_1ufnn_601\" data-testid=\"copy-button\" aria-label=\"Copy content\" title=\"Copy content\" data-analytics-funnel-value=\"button:r2s:\" type=\"submit\" data-analytics-performance-mark=\"7-1782459579395-4399\"><span class=\"awsui_icon_vjswe_1ufnn_630 awsui_icon-left_vjswe_1ufnn_630 awsui_icon_h11ix_3ufhe_189 awsui_size-normal-mapped-height_h11ix_3ufhe_248 awsui_size-normal_h11ix_3ufhe_244 awsui_variant-normal_h11ix_3ufhe_320\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 5H5v10h10V5Z\" class=\"stroke-linejoin-round\"></path><path d=\"M13 1H1v11\" class=\"stroke-linejoin-round\"></path></svg></span></button></span></span></div><p>（脚本 <code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">08-create-evaluators.sh</code> 已自动做这步预清理。）</p>"},{"type":"info","header":"","html":"<p>inference-profile（如 <code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">us.amazon.nova-2-lite-v1:0</code>）需同时授权 profile ARN 和底层 foundation-model ARN。</p>"},{"type":"success","header":"","html":"<p>两个评估器已上线! 下一步对 Phase 3 的对话跑一次评估,看 Agent 答得到底好不好。</p>"}]